# Trivy ignore file
#
# AVD-DS-0002 — "Image user should not be 'root'"
# The container image intentionally starts as root and drops privileges at
# runtime via gosu in docker/web-entrypoint.sh and docker/sidekiq-entrypoint.sh
# to support the optional PUID/PGID file-ownership feature. A static USER
# directive would break that runtime user switching, so this rule is suppressed.
AVD-DS-0002
